---
description: Cybersecurity Area 08 cyber resilience and specialized technology rules
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

Use static evidence only. Separate evidence, fact, inference, hypothesis, recommendation, confidence, limitation, owner, approver, and independent reviewer. Require qualified specialist review for high-impact OT/ICS, IoT, AI, hardware, firmware, cryptographic, or safety-relevant conclusions.
